audioanalyze.quickdescript: transcribe audio/video/links to text using openai whisper model

convert.quickdescript: converts a file to different format based on uploaded file type or specified in the command.

downloader.quickdescript: download video/audio from social/music platforms (YouTube, Twitter, Instagram, SoundCLoud, Spotify)\n\n*Spotify may not result with a correct song if its not found on youtube, if that happens, try finding it on youtube and send the link instead.*

lyricfinder.quickdescript: Fings lyrics for a song from music platforms (YouTube, Spotify, SoundCloud)

riodejaneiro.quickdescript: Adds a Rio De Janeiro instagram filter over image/video
